    "In our approach, polymers with an SA score below 5 are considered synthesizable 36.",
    "It's important to recognize that variations in the specific threshold for the SA score do not substantially influence the overall evaluation of synthesizability.",
    "We can also utilize the mean SA score which shows the same trend as the synthesizability as defined.",
